# TypeScript/React Native Testing

> This file extends [common/testing.md](../common/testing.md) with React Native specific content.

## Unit Testing

Use **Vitest** as the unit testing framework for components, hooks, and utilities.

```bash
# Run tests
cd client
npm test

# Run with coverage
npm test -- --coverage

# Watch mode
npm test -- --watch
```

## E2E Testing

Use **Detox** as the E2E testing framework for React Native mobile apps.

```bash
# Build for E2E
detox build --configuration android.emu.debug

# Run E2E tests
detox test --configuration android.emu.debug
```

